node.title: People evacuated from homes after Northland fire
node.description: Six properties were below the fire, which burnt through 5 hectares of vegetation.
node.content:
["A fire on a hill in Ahipara burnt through 5 hectares of vegetation before it was contained overnight.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "People from six properties below the fire had to be evacuated.", "Two helicopters and ground crews were dousing smouldering scrub and small flare-ups.", "The cause of the fire was being investigated."]
